# .gitignore — Anti-Gravity OS

# ─── Personal / Private ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Your personal version of GEMINI.md (contains your name, context, patterns)
# DO NOT commit the personal version. The repo ships with the generic template.
GEMINI-PERSONAL.md
MASTER-PROMPT-PERSONAL.md

# Personal memory files (your project-specific learnings — keep local)
# Uncomment these if you want memory to stay private:
# global/memory/decisions-log.md
# global/memory/mistakes-to-avoid.md
# global/memory/postmortems.md

# ─── Node / JS ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
node_modules/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
.npm
.pnp
.pnp.js

# ─── Python ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
*.so
.Python
build/
dist/
*.egg-info/
.eggs/
pip-log.txt
pip-delete-this-directory.txt
.venv
venv/
ENV/
env.bak/
.pytest_cache/

# ─── IDE / Editor ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.vscode/
.cursor/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# ─── OS ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
.DS_Store?
._*
.Spotlight-V100
.Trashes
ehthumbs.db
Desktop.ini

# ─── Credentials / Secrets ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.env
.env.*
*.key
*.pem
*.p12
*.pfx
secrets.json
credentials.json
gdrive-credentials/

# ─── Logs ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.log
logs/
brain/
scratch/

# ─── Temp / Build ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
tmp/
temp/
.temp/
.ruff_cache/
*.tmp

# ─── Large Files ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.pdf
*.zip
*.tar.gz
*.rar

# ─── AI System Internals (don't commit runtime state) ────────────────────────
context_state/
conversations/
html_artifacts/
browser_recordings/
knowledge/
implicit/
annotations/
code_tracker/
